(breathes rapidly)

331
00:24:06,654 --> 00:24:08,864
(breathes heavily)

332
00:24:12,076 --> 00:24:14,620
Wake up, Yesool.

333
00:24:15,371 --> 00:24:16,789
Yesool.

334
00:24:19,833 --> 00:24:21,794
(dramatic music)

335
00:24:29,760 --> 00:24:31,762
(breathes deeply)

336
00:24:49,780 --> 00:24:52,032
The same thing happened back then.

337
00:24:55,494 --> 00:24:57,246
Back then, he tried to save me...

338
00:25:00,749 --> 00:25:01,834
Yesool.

339
00:25:03,168 --> 00:25:05,254
Do you remember everything?

340
00:25:06,463 --> 00:25:08,674
(somber music)

341
00:25:21,145 --> 00:25:22,146
Yesool.

342
00:25:22,688 --> 00:25:23,772
Can you hear me?

343
00:25:24,898 --> 00:25:26,233
It's Mom.

