352
00:26:12,196 --> 00:26:14,782
You didn't remember what had happened
to your father that day,

353
00:26:15,574 --> 00:26:17,618
or Minhu's existence.

354
00:26:19,328 --> 00:26:21,038
I was glad

355
00:26:21,538 --> 00:26:23,248
that you had forgotten.

356
00:26:27,211 --> 00:26:28,462
But...

357
00:26:34,510 --> 00:26:35,636
Yesool.

358
00:26:37,137 --> 00:26:38,097
Let's...

359
00:26:39,723 --> 00:26:41,225
go to the United States.

360
00:26:44,978 --> 00:26:47,231
Remember your uncle's house?

361
00:26:48,273 --> 00:26:51,193
Let's go there and forget about all this.

362
00:26:51,276 --> 00:26:52,236
Mom.

363
00:26:54,363 --> 00:26:55,572
I've...

364
00:26:57,241 --> 00:26:58,867
known all along.

365
00:27:02,287 --> 00:27:04,289
(machine beeping)

366
00:27:04,998 --> 00:27:07,126
(line beeps)

367
00:27:15,968 --> 00:27:17,010
I...

368
